data.description: Discover the quaint charm of this three-bedroom, two-bath haven that whispers of untapped potential, poised for your tender love and care. Erected in 1983 just on the cusp of Decatur, this home is steeped in vintage allure and ready for a revitalizing touch. Occupying nearly an acre adorned with stalwart trees, the expansive fenced backyard is a haven for creative landscaping ventures. Featuring a snug galley kitchen and ample bedrooms, this property is an open invitation to those with a vision for transformation. Step in and imagine the possibilities. Please note that the dishwasher is inoperable.
